### Common Pitfalls

| Wrong | Right |
|-------|-------|
| `fn foo()` | `fun foo()` |
| `foo() -> int` | `foo() : int` |
| `if cond then expr else other` | `then` is NOT a keyword in hica â€” parse error. Use brace syntax: `if cond { expr } else { other }`. This applies to `else if` chains too: `if a { x } else if b { y } else { z }`. |
